title: Black Keys
description:
Black Keys, multilingual keyboards, for unsupported languages and typing IPA (International Phonetic Alphabet).
Black mode is simple but awesome and good for your eyes.

Check your language in this list and download:
*IPA: IPA full and English IPA (new design and full of letters)
*Arabic group: Persian/Farsi, Dari, Pashto,Sorani Kurdish, Uyghur
*Need to install font group: Aramaic Syriac, Amharic, Burmese, Coptic, Assyrian,N'ko,Tifinagh
*Others: Khmer, Inuktitut, Georgian, Armenian, Sinhala, Lao, Kazakh, Nepali, Bangla, Gurmukhi, Malayalam, Gujarati, Kannada, Oriya, Telugu.

*NOTE:
-Some keyboard have longPress to popup some hidden letters: Amharic, Aramaic, Assyrian, Dari, Persian, Pashto, Sorani Kurdish. Please take your time to practice much from beginning to understand how to use or check our video tutorials from app
-Burmese and Sinhala use smart combination to help you type faster, please check tutorial video from app.

If your keyboard miss some letters, or need to improve or you need to add your languages,please contact us on Facebook:

*Native speaker write for Persian/Farsi
